summary: This simply makes it so that every time you punch (unarmed) you yell Falcon Punch.
descriptionHtml:
Just a simple mod i came up with my friends and we thought it would be funny to do. This simply makes it so that every time you punch (unarmed) you yell Falcon Punch.  I plan on making it replace Fus Ro Dah when i figure out where the audio files are for that.

Simply extract file into skyrim data folder and your done!
author: Kingbeast
